<p>'The mugger had a gun pointed at my mother's head. There were two gunmen. It happened at 8:30 pm just as the sun was going down.'</p>

<p>Cheban also told DailyMail.com this week that though he talked to police who had sketches of the criminals made up, the attackers have not been caught yet. </p>

<p>Last week Jonathan said he does not want to be in New York City these days, even though the incident happened in New Jersey. </p>

